description: This multiple-choice game is a fun way to challenge what you know about the movie Old School.  Think you have what it takes to get a perfect score?  Think you can score more points than your know-it-all friend?  ...then put your knowledge to the test.  Please note this game contains material that may not be suitable for young children; parental discretion is advised.
